- Status: The spymaster Nahkriin's operations continue. Esbern has been rescued from the Ratway Warrens (Thalmor squad eliminated), but the location is compromised. Esbern is currently with the cart at the camp outside Forelhost, urging the party to retrieve the Dragonstone from Bleak Falls Barrow to map the dragon graves.
