- Status: Valerius Caelus works from Solitude to establish a vampire aristocracy. The Dark Brotherhood seeks a resurgence through the contract to assassinate the Emperor. Orion sits as the fulcrum, carrying the Ring of the Pale Regent while trying to manage faction standing and initiate into the Brotherhood.

